data.description: Ranch with Endless Potential! Step into this delightful ranch home with a partially finished basement and be greeted by double front doors leading to a bright foyer. Enjoy a dining room, a cozy living room, and a versatile sitting area that's currently being used as an office. With 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, there's plenty of space for your family. Situated on a spacious half-acre lot, the backyard offers a gorgeous view of farmland. Plus, you'll find ample storage in the basement and room for potential expansion.This home in a beautiful neighborhood is waiting for your personal touch. Contact me today to explore the possibilities!
